These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
City: boston, london
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, teacher
1. the mechanic is in an even position##4
2. the teacher is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| City   | london | boston |
| Job     | teacher    | mechanic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: french, american
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the american is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Nationality   | american | french        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, february
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Birthday   | february    | october |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daisy
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | 7up      | lemonade |
| Flower       | dahlia | daisy    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
