.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-8::.
2 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble
2 different pets are kept: dog, frog
1. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Game   | backgammon | scrabble |
| Pet           | frog       | dog       |

